reviewText: At last, the long awaited sequel to the 60's Japanese import is finally available on Blu-ray. However it is only in Japanese, and requires a multi-region Blu-ray player. ( See Amazon listings for one) Very well done , the Science Patrol is now called MATS, and all new actors and actresses fill out the team. New equipment, and a new Ultraman round out the cast. Oh, I almost forgot, all new monsters, too!
